  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to explore the experience in being with advanced Heart failure
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim is to explore the experience of advanced Heart failure patients during the disease
      trajectory in Taiwan.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
